      <title>Re: Fantastic solution! Simple and functional t...</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/owsimpleoperator/forum/general/fantastic_solution_simple_and_functional_to_use/re_fantastic_solution_simple_and_functional_t4</link>
      <description>Thanks for this extension, helped me a lot. I just wished I would have found this extension before I wasted some hours trying to derive my own operator from other template extensions. With your basis it has been a matter of minutes.&#13;
&#13;
So simple, yet I failed deriving this from the SwarkTemplate extension :(&#13;
&#13;
&lt;code&gt;&#13;
&lt;?php&#13;
&#13;
class FirstTrueOperator extends OWSimpleOperator&#13;
{&#13;
    &#13;
    public function first_true( $value1, $value2, $value3, $value4, $value5, $value6, $value7, $value8, $value9, $value10 )&#13;
    {&#13;
        $arg_list = func_get_args();&#13;
		for ($i = 0; $i &lt; func_num_args(); $i++) {&#13;
			if ($arg_list[$i]) {&#13;
				return $arg_list[$i];&#13;
			} &#13;
		}&#13;
    }&#13;
    &#13;
}&#13;
?&gt;&#13;
&lt;/code&gt;</description>
