      <title>Fantastic solution! Simple and functional to use</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/owsimpleoperator/forum/general/fantastic_solution_simple_and_functional_to_use</link>
      <description>Hello Thomas,&#13;
&#13;
Thank you very much for publishing your complete extension here on projects.ez.no&#13;
&#13;
I really believe this extension will extend an amazingly powerful influence for good to each of it's users. It's rare that I am really impressed with a new extension, today I was with yours.&#13;
&#13;
eZ Publish developers looking to more quickly expose more powerful PHP user defined functions as an eZ Publish Template operator. Folks are always looking for ways to call PHP operators which require more than one parameter (limitation) in eZ Publish Templates, I think this extension can really help users realize these goals quickly with little trouble. New eZ Publish developers, get your copy while it's fresh, this is the best!&#13;
&#13;
Also a personal thank you for licensing your extension under the GNU GPL. A lot of people really believe in the value it shares to all who come into contact with it.&#13;
&#13;
I can't wait to see what you create with eZ Publish next! :)&#13;
&#13;
Best wishes&#13;
&#13;
Cheers,&#13;
Heath</description>
